M / F, Bac +5, engineering school or Master, minimum 2 years of experience in Data Engineering, with solid skills in the following areas:
Mastery of the PYTHON language: application development and integration of applications in Big Data environments;
Competitive programming for real-time application;
Development and use of APIs;
Network flow management (SSH, SFTP/FTP);
Experience in a Big Data environment (e.g. Google Cloud Platform,...);
Mastery of the Linux environment: knowledge of the necessary shell bases;
Good knowledge of statistics;
Appetite for algorithms;
Fluent English (both written and spoken);
Training in data science is a plus: integration of machine learning modules, development of new models.
Knowledge of the telecoms/network sector, media and/or innovative services is a plus.
